6726 - Unit Investment Trusts, Face-Amount Certificate Offices and Closed-End Management Investment Offices Summary > SENTINEL PROPERTY GROUP PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover unit investment trusts, face-amount certificate & closed-end mgmt investment offices. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. SENTINEL PROPERTY GROUP PTY LTD is headquartered in Brisbane, Queensland. It is headed by CEO, managing dir & company sec Warren James Ebert. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $34.21 million. Its net profit totalled $9.56 million. SENTINEL PROPERTY GROUP PTY LTD forms part of the finance, insurance, and real estate industry sector.
